description: A one-click BusyBox installation utility for Android! BusyBox Installer is a one-click BusyBox installation utility for various android architectures (ARM/ARM64 and x86). WARNING: I Am NOT Responsible for any Damages on Your Device! BusyBox Installer requires ROOT Access. Features * An easy BusyBox installation for ARM/ARM64 and x86. * Removal of BusyBox applets (only) installed by this app. * Show applets list (only) installed by this app. * Dark and Light themes (depends on system theme). Translations Please help me to translate this application via POEditor. You may also translate after downloading the original language string available GitHub.
